By abuse of notation, $\Phi$ and $\Psi$ will also denote their natural extensions of the form $\SP(V)\rightarrow \SP(V\wedge V)$. We thus obtain a square of maps \begin{equation}\label{eq:diagdeltasigmaphipsi}
