\begin{proposition} The diagram \ref{eq:diagdeltasigmaphipsi} with $\Psi$ commutes, that is $\Psi\circ \sigma=(\sigma\triangle \sigma) \circ \Delta$.
\end{proposition}
\begin{proof}
